metadata.title: Legrand - C2G HDMI VGA and AUX Wall Pass Through, Pass Through Wall Plate for In Wall Cable Management, Brushed Aluminium, Silver, 1 Count, C2G 60144
features: HDMI VGA and AUX Wall Pass Through - One (1) Aluminum Single Gang Pass Through Wall Plate
Use - Install this HDMI VGA and AUX wall plate to pass HDMI 2. 0, VGA, and 3. 5mm AUX signals through the wall for high quality video and audio signals between your components
Optimal In Wall Cabling - These flexible HDMI and 3. 5mm AUX pigtail plugs make routing cables behind the wall a breeze for the best in wall cable management
Durable - Built from aluminum for a sturdy and attractive finish to your outlet, this in wall cable management is the perfect solution for both home and office settings
Compatibility - This C2G pass through wall plate is compatible with standard single gang wall boxes and is easy to install over existing boxes with just a screwdriver
description: This wall plate is an ideal solution for installations which require that a Blu-ray player and a computer be connected to a projector through in-wall cabling. This wall plate features flexible HDMI and 3. 5mm pigtails which makes installing this wall plate in a wall box easier than wall plates which require use of standard HDMI and 3. 5mm cables. This wall plate is designed to work with standard wall boxes and the aluminum construction provides durability and a long life.
